. <em>Lancet</em> 1994;343(8899): 692–695.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0140-6736(94)91578-4">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7907678/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Risks+of+cancer+in+BRCA1-mutation+carriers%3A+Breast+Cancer+Linkage+Consortium&amp;author=D+Ford&amp;author=DF+Easton&amp;author=DT+Bishop&amp;author=SA+Narod&amp;author=DE+Goldgar&amp;publication_year=1994&amp;journal=Lancet&amp;pages=692-695&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS0140-6736%2894%2991578-4&amp;pmid=7907678">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Domchek S, Weber BL. Genetic variants of uncertain significance: flies in the ointment. <em>J Clin Oncol</em> 2008;26(1): 16–17.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1200/JCO.2007.14.4154">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18165634/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Genetic+variants+of+uncertain+significance%3A+flies+in+the+ointment&amp;author=S+Domchek&amp;author=BL+Weber&amp;publication_year=2008&amp;journal=J+Clin+Oncol&amp;pages=16-17&amp;doi=10.1200%2FJCO.2007.14.4154&amp;pmid=18165634">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Ford D, Easton DF, Peto J. Estimates of the gene frequency of BRCA1 and its contribution to breast and ovarian cancer incidence. <em>Am J Hum Genet</em> 1995;57(6):1457–1462.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8533776/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Estimates+of+the+gene+frequency+of+BRCA1+and+its+contribution+to+breast+and+ovarian+cancer+incidence&amp;author=D+Ford&amp;author=DF+Easton&amp;author=J+Peto&amp;publication_year=1995&amp;journal=Am+J+Hum+Genet&amp;pages=1457-1462&amp;pmid=8533776">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">8.</div><div id="r8" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Whittemore AS, Gong G, John EM, et al. Prevalence of BRCA1 mutation carriers among U.S. non-Hispanic whites. <em>Cancer Epidemiol Biomarkers Prev</em> 2004;13(12): 2078–2083.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15598764/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Prevalence+of+BRCA1+mutation+carriers+among+U.S.+non-Hispanic+whites&amp;author=AS+Whittemore&amp;author=G+Gong&amp;author=EM+John&amp;publication_year=2004&amp;journal=Cancer+Epidemiol+Biomarkers+Prev&amp;pages=2078-2083&amp;pmid=15598764">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">9.</div><div id="r9" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Siegel RL, Miller KD, Jemal A. Cancer statistics, 2016. <em>CA Cancer J Clin</em> 2016;66(1):7–30.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.3322/caac.21332">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26742998/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Cancer+statistics%2C+2016&amp;author=RL+Siegel&amp;author=KD+Miller&amp;author=A+Jemal&amp;publication_year=2016&amp;journal=C